@startuml identity-lifecycle
title Person Identity Lifecycle

[*] --> Provisional : Self-Registration / Field Capture

Provisional --> Verified : Case Worker Confirms NIC/Biometrics
Provisional --> Rejected : Duplicate Detected / Invalid IDs

state Verified {
  [*] --> Active
  Active --> Restricted : Legal/Compliance Hold
  Restricted --> Active : Hold Lifted
}

Verified --> Merged : Duplicate found post-verification
Merged --> [*] : Pointer to Master Record

@enduml
